short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The Tidelift extension is a tool for exploring Tidelift data about open source packages and releases on github.com

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension augments open source package repository pages on github.com with Tidelift recommendation data to help our customers choose high-quality packages and avoid known issues.  Requires a subscription to the Tidelift platform.
